title: Each node gets a different ID
gherkin:
When the user creates a set of 10 "<node type>"s
Then each node in the response should contain a different ID

Examples:
  | node type     |
  | COMPANY       |
  | BRAND         |
  | CAR MODEL     |
  | RACE TRACK    |
  | TRACK LAYOUT  |
  | RACING SERIES |
  | RACING EVENT  |
  | IMAGE         |
